body.transcript:
Hello! My name is Sarah, and I am with RT 6 Boozers. How can I assist you today?

Hi Sarah! I'm calling because I had an issue during my last visit.

I'm sorry to hear that! Can I have your name, please, so I can help you better?

Sure, it's Jessica.

Thank you, Jessica! Could you please tell me the date of your visit?

It was on the fifteenth of October.

Thank you for that information! And could you also provide me with your email address?

It's jessica.smith@example.com.

Perfect! I've noted your details. Could you explain the issue you faced during your visit?

Yes, I had trouble getting service and it took a very long time.

I apologize for that experience, Jessica. Your feedback is invaluable. I will ensure it is addressed. Thank you for your time!
